  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our community by adding our game to your wishlist! Be part of this amazing journey and stay updated on all the latest news! ❤️<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/803972c7b41b581271f74267fe940ed2.poster.avif?t=1750305393\" width=612 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/803972c7b41b581271f74267fe940ed2.webm?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/803972c7b41b581271f74267fe940ed2.mp4?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/14ab4219a033520925640ae10a010661.poster.avif?t=1750305393\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/14ab4219a033520925640ae10a010661.webm?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/14ab4219a033520925640ae10a010661.mp4?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/7bbdc5fb77b3f85226789916e92ad3f9.poster.avif?t=1750305393\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/7bbdc5fb77b3f85226789916e92ad3f9.webm?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/7bbdc5fb77b3f85226789916e92ad3f9.mp4?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Broken World: Save Your Children is a survival game where you play as Josh, a father trying to keep his children, Edrik and Emma, alive in the midst of a zombie apocalypse. Your goal: make your way through a ruined city to the airport, where your wife awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage thirst, hunger, and happiness. Build weapons, traps, and shelters. Explore, fish, cook, and fight to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision matters. Will you risk everything for supplies or play it safe? Teach your children to fend for themselves or protect every step? In a broken world, a father's love is your greatest weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/99fee4024b62daff4ae0c5ed8c8be921.avif?t=1750305393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras_big/99fee4024b62daff4ae0c5ed8c8be921.avif?t=1750305393 width=800 height=532 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/7bbdc5fb77b3f85226789916e92ad3f9.poster.avif?t=1750305393\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/7bbdc5fb77b3f85226789916e92ad3f9.webm?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/7bbdc5fb77b3f85226789916e92ad3f9.mp4?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Broken World: Save Your Children is a survival game where you play as Josh, a father trying to keep his children, Edrik and Emma, alive in the midst of a zombie apocalypse. Your goal: make your way through a ruined city to the airport, where your wife awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage thirst, hunger, and happiness. Build weapons, traps, and shelters. Explore, fish, cook, and fight to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision matters. Will you risk everything for supplies or play it safe? Teach your children to fend for themselves or protect every step? In a broken world, a father's love is your greatest weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/99fee4024b62daff4ae0c5ed8c8be921.avif?t=1750305393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras_big/99fee4024b62daff4ae0c5ed8c8be921.avif?t=1750305393 width=800 height=532 /></span></p>",
